The '''Marauders' Masquerade''' was one of the three largest balls of the year among the [[Hapan]]s living on [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]] and in the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]]. It was outranked in prominence only by the [[Queen Mother's Birthday]].

